%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fisro-s-new-rocket-soorya-at-93-metres-taller-than-qutab-minar-840093%5C%22%3EScientist%20V%20Narayanan%20Speaks%20To%20NDTV%20About%20ISRO's%20'Soorya'%20Rocket%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20distinguished%20scientist%20(APEX%20Scale)%20and%20seniormost%20director%20in%20ISRO.%20The%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%2C%20which%20he%20heads%2C%20is%20engaged%20in%20the%20development%20of%20liquid%2C%20semi-cryogenic%20and%20cryogenic%20propulsion%20stages%20for%20launch%20vehicles%2C%20chemical%20and%20electric%20propulsion%20systems%20for%20satellites%2C%20control%20systems%20for%20launch%20vehicles%2C%20and%20transducers%20development%20for%20space%20systems%20health%20monitoring.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Project%20Management%20Council-Space%20Transportation%20System%20(PMC-STS)%2C%20the%20decision-making%20body%20in%20all%20launch%20vehicle%20projects%20and%20programmes%2C%20and%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Level%20Human%20Rated%20Certification%20Board%20(HRCB)%20for%20Gaganyaan%2C%20India's%20planned%20human%20spaceflight%20mission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20studied%20in%20Tamil-medium%20schools%2C%20Mr%20Narayanan%20chief%20completed%20his%20M%20Tech%20in%20Cryogenic%20Engineering%20and%20PhD%20in%20Aerospace%20Engineering%20from%20IIT%2C%20Kharagpur%2C%20where%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20Silver%20Medal%20for%20achieving%20the%20first%20rank%20in%20the%20M%20Tech%20programme.%20The%20rocket%20and%20spacecraft%20propulsion%20expert%20joined%20ISRO%20in%201984%20and%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20become%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Somanath%20took%20over%20as%20the%20ISRO%20chief%20in%20January%202022%20and%20it%20was%20under%20him%20that%20India%20became%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20land%20a%20rover%20in%20the%20south%20pole%20region%20of%20the%20Moon.%20It%20also%20joined%20an%20elite%20club%20of%20countries%20to%20achieve%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%20after%20the%20US%2C%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736301180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fh4rk0cto_v-narayanan_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fv-narayanan-appointed-new-isro-chief-will-replace-s-somanath-7422942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20appointed%20V%20Narayanan%20as%20the%20new%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20and%20secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Space.%20Mr%20Narayanan%20will%20take%20over%20from%20S%20Somanath%2C%20the%20current%20head%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20on%20January%2014.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fv-narayanan-appointed-new-isro-chief-will-replace-s-somanath-7422942%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'All%20hell%20will%20break%20out'%3A%20Trump%20warns%20Hamas%20over%20hostages%20crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736301143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117038182%2Cimgsize-872752.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fall-hell-will-break-out-in-the-middle-east-trump-warns-hamas-over-hostages-crisis%2Farticleshow%2F117038084.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President-elect%20Trump%20has%20issued%20a%20stern%20warning%20to%20Hamas%2C%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20by%20his%20inauguration%20on%20January%2020%2C%20or%20threatening%20severe%20consequences.%20His%20warnings%20hint%20at%20significant%20actions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20if%20demands%20are%20not%20met.%20The%20situation%20remains%20uncertain%20with%20ongoing%20negotiations%20involving%2