r.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Gambhir%20was%20appointed%20head%20coach%20across%20all%20formats%2C%20India%20dominated%20the%20shortest%20format%20of%20the%20game%20but%20have%20struggled%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Following%20a%202-0%20home%20series%20win%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20following%20which%20it%20seemed%20India%20had%20all%20but%20sealed%20a%20spot%20in%20their%20third%20consecutive%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final.%20However%2C%20a%20humiliating%200-3%20loss%20against%20New%20Zealand%20followed%2C%20which%20was%20the%20nation's%20first%20home-series%20defeat%20in%2012%20years.%20India%20were%20eliminated%20from%20WTC%20contention%20following%20the%20loss%20in%20the%20BGT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20host%20England%20for%20a%20white-ball%20series%20--%20five%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20starting%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20January%20before%20they%20leave%20for%20Dubai%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20Champions%20Trophy.%20India's%20next%20Test%20assignment%20will%20be%20the%20five-match%20Test%20series%20away%20in%20England%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736300940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fv48ovkfg_gambhir-rohit-bumrah-afp_625x300_06_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fbcci-to-review-australia-debacle-report-says-gautam-gambhir-will-survive-while-virat-kohli-and-rohit-sharma-7422594%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20have%20been%20a%20vital%20part%20and%20mainstay%20of%20India's%20top-order%20for%20the%20past%20decade%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Buy%20or%20sell%3A%20Stocks%20on%20brokerages%E2%