Cp%3ETo%20capture%20that%20kind%20of%20information%2C%20a%20plane%20flies%20over%20an%20area%20and%20the%20lidar%20sensor%20emits%20millions%20of%20pulses%20of%20light%20that%20are%20used%20to%20measure%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20plane%20and%20the%20objects%20below.%20Some%20light%20slips%20between%20the%20tree%20canopy%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20which%20can%20reveal%20forgotten%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dataset%20covered%20an%20area%20of%20Campeche%20in%20Southeastern%20Mexico%20where%20Lowland%20Maya%20civilizations%20once%20flourished.%20However%2C%20the%20area%20is%20so%20dense%20with%20trees%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20see%20structures%20from%20the%20sky.%20Archaeologists%20had%20never%20studied%20this%20particular%20spot%2C%20so%20Auld-Thomas%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20the%20data%20would%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turned%20out%20that%20there%20were%20thousands%20of%20structures%20under%20the%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20locals%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20ruins%20nearby%2C%20but%20the%20scientific%20community%20had%20no%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20Marcello%20Canuto%2C%20a%20Tulane%20University%20professor%20and%20Auld-Thomas'%20advisor%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20researchers%20were%20surprised%20to%20find%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20settlements%20at%20the%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lidar%20images%20of%20bumpy%20structures%20with%20labels%20including%20ballcourt%2C%20dam%2C%20and%20houses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676dab2ca3e82c7912047432%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221161%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELidar%20images%20of%20Valeriana%2C%20a%20hidden%20city%20in%20Mexico.%3Cp%3ELuke%20Auld-Thomas%2FTulane%20University%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Auld-Thomas%20and%20Marcello%20started%20looking%20at%20the%20lidar%20data%2C%20they%20were%20surprised%20to%20see%20