they%20were%20seen%20together%20inside%20the%20DNP%20closure%20(Sudashri%20area).%20In%20October%20and%20February%202023%2C%20nine%20birds%20were%20seen%20together%20inside%20the%20DNP%20area.%20This%20(latest)%20photo%20shows%20the%20results%20of%20the%20efforts%20being%20taken%20to%20protect%20the%20endangered%20state%20bird.%20It%20also%20shows%20the%20need%20and%20importance%20of%20the%20closure%20made%20within%20the%20DNP%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20(DCF)%20Ashish%20Vyas%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GIB%20is%20a%20highly%20endangered%20bird%20species%20found%20in%20the%20Thar%20area%20of%20Rajasthan.%20Today%2C%20only%20173%20birds%20are%20left%2C%20of%20which%2C%20128%20are%20found%20in%20the%20wild%20and%20the%20remaining%20are%20bred%20in%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20bird%20is%20found%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202011%2C%20the%20birds%20were%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3Bcritically%20endangered%26quot%3B%20by%20IUCN%20Red%20List.%20(Dr%20Ashish%20Vyas%2C%20DCF%2C%20Desert%20National%20Park)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22In%202011%2C%20the%20birds%20were%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3Bcritically%20endangered%26quot%3B%20by%20IUCN%20Red%20List.%20(Dr%20Ashish%20Vyas%2C%20DCF%2C%20Desert%20National%20Park)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F7fk7mls8_great-indian-bustard_625x300_07_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%20birds%20were%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3Bcritically%20endangered%26quot%3B%20by%20IUCN%20Red%20List.%20(Dr%20Ashish%20Vyas%2C%20DCF%2C%20Desert%20National%20Park)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%20GIBs%20were%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3Bcritically%20endangered%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20threat%20-%20by%20the%20International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature%20(IUCN)%20Red%20List.%20According%20to%20IUCN%2C%20hunting%2C%20disturbance%2C%20habitat%20loss%20and%20fragmentation%20were%20among%20factors%20that%20had%20reduced%20the%20population%20of%20these%20magnificent%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20Rajasthan%20became%20the%20first%20state%20to%20launch%20a%20Rs%2012.90%20crore%20worth%20project%20to%20save%20the%20GIB.%20The%20state%20adopted%20a%20two-pronged%20strategy%20to%20conserve%20the%20species%20-%20protect%20its%20natural%20habitat%20and%20improve%20conditions%20for%20breeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%2045%20chicks%20have%20been%20bred%20in%20two%20sites%20-%20one%20in%20Sam%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Ramdevra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20birds%20that%20were%20spotted%20together%20on%20Monday%20were%20born%20in%20the%20wild.%20They%20are%20mostly%20females%2C%20about%20three%20to%20four%20years%20old.%20Some%20of%20them%20may%20also%20be%20males%20of%20up%20to%20one%20year%20of%20age.%20We%20protect%20these%20birds%20by%20improving%20the%20grasslands%2C%20which%20are%20their%20natural%20habitat.%20These%20birds%20are%20omnivorous%20and%20feed%20on%20insects%20and%20desert%20fruits.%20So%2C%20when%20their%20habitat%20is%20improved%2C%20they%20have%20enough%20food.%20We%20also%20fence%20the%20areas%20they%20are%20found%20in%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20predators%20like%20the%20desert%20fox%2C%20the%20desert%20cat%20and%20the%20mongoose%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vyas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20birds%20lay%20their%20eggs%20in%20the%20ground%20but%20the%20eggs%20are%20often%20carried%20away%20by%20the%20predators.%20By%20fencing%20their%20habitat%2C%20we%20ensure%20that%20they%20can%20successfully%20breed%20in%20the%20wild.%20They%20are%20also%20protected%20from%20cattle%20that%20often%20stray%20into%20these%20grasslands.%20The%20fenced%20areas%20are%20patrolled%20by%20the%20field%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20in%20October%2C%20the%20state%20government's%20GIB%20conservation%20programme%20touched%20another%20milestone%20when%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20scientists%20at%20the%20National%20Conservation%20Breeding%20Centre%20in%20Jaisalmer%20hatched%20a%20GIB%20chick%20through%20artificial%20insemination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20little%20chick%2C%20a%20male%2C%20is%20now%20nearly%20four%20months%20old%20and%20has%20been%20named%20%26quot%3BArambh%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Wildlife%20Institute%20of%20India%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Government%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20Forest%20Department%2C%20established%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Bustard%20Artificial%20Breeding%20Center%20in%20Jaisalmer%20under%20the%20Bustard%20Recovery%20Program.%20The%20programme%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20GIB%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736273640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fojhre5s_great-indian-bustards_625x300_07_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-rare-sighting-12-endangered-great-indian-bustards-spotted-together-in-rajasthan-7422705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2012%20Great%20Indian%20Bustards%20were%20spotted%20in%20a%20group%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20in%20a%20major%20boost%20to%20efforts%20to%20conserve%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20critically%20endangered%20species.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-rare-sighting-12-endangered-great-indian-bustards-spotted-together-in-rajasthan-7422705%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Advik%20to%20acquire%20German%20braking%20system%20manufacturer%20Powersports%20MTG%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736273502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F