ecent%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20According%20to%20Anderson%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20X%20is%20forgetting%20the%20%26quot%3Bcore%20tenets%20of%20journalism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...Without%20them%2C%20I%20think%20your%20efforts%20to%20make%20X%20the%20respected%20home%20of%20citizen%20journalism%20will%20fail.%20When%20you%20tell%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20that%20someone%20should%20be%20hanged%20or%20jailed%20for%20outrageous%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20just%20possibly%20you%20should%20first%20sound%20out%20what%20those%20who%20know%20those%20people%20really%20well%20would%20say%20about%20them.%20Some%20of%20your%20recent%20posts%20could%20literally%20get%20someone%20killed.%20Do%20you%20really%20want%20to%20risk%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20questioned%2C%20referring%20to%20Musk's%20recent%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20been%20frequently%20bashing%20international%20governments%20whose%20politics%20he%20dislikes%20and%20praising%20far-right%20figures.%20He%20has%20been%20using%20X%20to%20post%20several%20criticisms%20and%20accusations%20aimed%20at%20political%20figures%20-%20especially%20in%20UK%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20say%20you%20want%20to%20maximize%20un-regretted%20user%20seconds%20on%20X.%20%C2%A0By%20far%20the%20simplest%20way%20you%20could%20do%20this%2C%20Elon%2C%20is%20simply%20to%20thoughtfully%20edit%20what%20you%20yourself%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Anderson%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20X%20is%20failing%20to%20follow%20the%20%26quot%3Bfairness%20doctrine%26quot%3B%20-%20which%20says%20that%20before%20publishing%20critical%20claims%20about%20an%20individual%2C%20or%20an%20institution%2C%20one%20must%20reach%20out%20to%20them%20for%20their%20side%20of%20the%20story.%20While%20the%20TED%20chief%20believes%20that%20Musk%20is%20eyeing%20issues%20that%20are%20important%20and%20worthy%20of%20efforts%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20way%20it%20is%20being%20presented%20is%20%26quot%3Bplayground%20bullying%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20crass%20and%20it's%20cruel%2C%20and%20it's%20therefore%20not%20nearly%20as%20effective%20as%20it%20could%20be.%20You're%20hearing%20the%20cheers%20of%20your%20most%20loyal%20followers%2C%20but%20missing%20the%20fact%20you're%20making%20yourself%20a%20laughing%20stock%20among%20many%20who%20you%20really%20want%20on%20your%20side.%20Long-term%20that's%20going%20to%20damage%20X%2C%20your%20other%20businesses%2C%20and%20indeed%20your%20long-term%20dreams%20for%20humanity.%20%C2%A0No%20one%20wants%20to%20follow%20a%20playground%20bully%20to%20Mars%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20trepidation%2C%20I'm%20posting%20this%20open%20letter%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40elonmusk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20someone%20I%20have%20admired%2C%20but%20who%2C%20right%20now%2C%20is%20causing%20me%20concern.%20I%20know%20I'm%20not%20alone%20in%20thinking%20these%20thoughts.%20Please%20like%20or%20repost%20if%20you're%20willing...%20And%20Elon%2C%20if%20you're%20listening%2C%20please%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWGU9okIXJ3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FWGU9okIXJ3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Chris%20Anderson%20(%40TEDchris)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTEDchris%2Fstatus%2F1876602909590192213%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnderson%20mentioned%20that%20while%20Musk%20is%20someone%20he%20admires%2C%20at%20present%2C%20he%20is%20causing%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20miss%20the%20old%20Elon.%20You%20can%20be%20funny%2C%20interesting%2C%20insightful%20and%20inspiring.%20You've%20fought%20incredibly%20hard%20for%20what%20you've%20built.%20And%20you%20may%20feel%20you're%20entitled%20to%20do%20whatever%20the%20hell%20you%20want%20with%20it.%20But%20I%20also%20know%20that%20you%20understand%20the%20danger%20of%20holding%20too%20tightly%20to%20the%20ring%20of%20power%2C%20how%20it%20can%20distort%20someone's%20judgement%20and%20turn%20them%20ugly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20hoping%20you%20can%20loosen%20that%20ring%20just%20a%20little.%20For%20the%20love%20of%20humanity%20that%20you%20profess%2C%20I%20really%20urge%20you%20to%20embrace%20the%20fairness%20doctrine%20and%20showcase%20a%20better%20face%20of%20X%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736268360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fia9vj4do_musk-chris_625x300_07_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyour-posts-could-get-someone-killed-ted-chief-chris-anderson-to-elon-musk-7422265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20has%20been%20frequently%20bashing%20international%20governments%20whose%20politics%20he%20dislikes%20and%20praising%20far-right%20figures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyour-posts-could-get-someone-killed-ted-chief-chris-anderson-to-elon-musk-7422265%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Steel's%20crude%20steel%20production%20rises%206%25%20to%205.68%20mn%20tonnes%20in%20Q3FY25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736268339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-steel-s-crude-steel-production-rises-6-to-5-68-mn-tonnes-in-q3fy25-125010701320_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deliveries%20in%20India%20reached%205.29%20MT%20for%20the%20third%20quarter%2C