uard%20are%20also%20often%20transported%20on%20foot%20or%20bikes%20instead%20of%20in%20one%20convoy%20to%20ensure%20that%20Maoists%20don't%20get%20a%20single%20target.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'%3Cstrong%3EUnder%20Review'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBijapur%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Jitendra%20Yadav%20confirmed%20that%20the%20incident%20is%20under%20review%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Maoists%20keep%20changing%20their%20tactics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20of%20the%20blast%20was%20very%20high.%20The%20road-opening%20party%20and%20demining%20team%20were%20deployed%2C%20so%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20IED%20blast%20are%20being%20investigated.%20SOPs%20were%20followed%2C%20but%20Naxalites%20continuously%20change%20their%20tactics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20attack%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20had%20said%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20had%20already%20begun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20thorough%20investigation%20and%20assessment%20of%20this%20attack%20are%20underway.%20I%20assure%20you%20that%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20our%20soldiers%20will%20not%20go%20in%20vain.%20The%20government%20is%20fully%20committed%20to%20eradicating%20Naxalism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736266920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fus8jk70o_maoist-attack_625x300_06_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-abujhmad-naxal-attack-how-was-60-kg-bomb-missed-after-bastar-maoist-attack-questions-on-lapses-7422126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20use%20of%20an%20improvised%20explosive%20device%20by%20Maoists%20to%20kill%20eight%20police%20personnel%20and%20a%20civilian%20driver%2C%20carrying%20out%20their%20largest%20strike%20in%20two%20years%20and%20the%20first%20major%20assault%20of%202025%2C%20has%20raised%20a%20series%20of%20questions%20about%20possible%20lapses.%22%2C%22aut