ue%20to%20the%20ongoing%20collision%20of%20the%20Indian%20and%20Eurasian%20tectonic%20plates%2C%20a%20process%20that's%20been%20shaping%20the%20Himalayas%20for%20the%20past%2060%20million%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETibet%20has%20seen%20several%20earthquakes%20in%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20including%20a%20magnitude%208.6%20quake%20in%201950.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20plate%2C%20which%20collided%20with%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%2C%20is%20slowly%20peeling%20apart%20beneath%20Tibet%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fessopenarchive.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.22541%2Fessoar.170000377.75686509%2Fv1%5C%22%3Estudy%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0last%20year.%20This%20%26quot%3Bslab%20tear%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20process%20where%20the%20upper%20crust%20of%20the%20Indian%20plate%20detaches%20from%20its%20denser%20lower%20layer%2C%20creating%20significant%20seismic%20activity%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tearing%20process%20could%20divide%20Tibet%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20likely%20to%20cause%20a%20visible%20crack%20on%20the%20surface.%20The%20tear%20comes%20deep%20beneath%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20and%20may%20influence%20seismic%20activity%20in%20the%20region.%20Scientists%20are%20studying%20earthquake%20waves%2C%20deep-layer%20earthquakes%2C%20and%20gas%20emissions%20to%20understand%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20this%20tectonic%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Himalayas%20remain%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20geologically%20active%20zones%2C%20with%20a%20history%20of%20significant%20earthquakes.%20Scientists%20warn%20that%20the%20ongoing%20collision%20of%20the%20plates%20continues%20to%20amplify%20seismic%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20strong%20tremors%20were%20reported%20as%20far%20as%20Kathmandu%2C%20Nepal%2C%20400%20km%20from%20the%20epicentre%2C%20although%20the%20country%20reported%20no%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20urged%20comprehensive%20efforts%20to%20minimise%20casualties%20and%20ensure%20proper%20resettlement.%20Emergency%20response%20teams%20are%20working%20to%20address%20the%20disaster's%20aftermath%20while%20aftershocks%20rattle%20the%20region.%20China%20has%20closed%20the%20tourist%20areas%20on%20its%20side%20of%20Mount%20Everest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736266260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmcllop3_tibetnepal-border-earthquake_625x300_07_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftibet-earthquake-linked-to-tectonic-stress-in-lhasa-block-7420667%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20powerful%20earthquake%20struck%20Tibet%20near%20Mount%20Everest%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20killing%20at%20least%20126%20people%20and%20injuring%20over%20130.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftibet-earthquake-linked-to-tectonic-stress-in-lhasa-block-7420667%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ros%20Atkins%20on...Elon%20Musk's%20political%20interventions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736266158000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ff46d%2Flive%2F130959a0-cd12-11ef-87df-d575b9a434a4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc0j1x6vy8v6o%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC's%20Analysis%20Editor%20looks%20at%20Elon%20Musk's%20involvement%20in%20politics%20outside%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc0j1x6vy8v6o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Keeping%20Tab%20On%20Number%20Of%20HMPV%20Cases%20%26quot%3BMeaningless%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-WHO%20Chief%20Scientist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnly%203%25%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20tested%20for%20Influenza-Like%20Illnesses%20(ILI)%20or%20Severe%20Acute%20Respiratory%20Illnesses%20(SARI)%20are%20found%20infected%20with%20the%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%2C%20which%20has%20triggered%20concerns%20five%20years%20after%20COVID-19%20first%20emerged%2C%20former%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20chief%20scientist%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Ms%20Swaminathan%20also%20said%20the%20HMPV%20infection%20has%20been%20in%20circulation%20in%20India%20for%20several%20years%2C%20but%20has%20come%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbit%20of%20shock%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20people%20as%20it%20is%20not%20frequently%20talked%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20health%20scientist's%20remarks%20came%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fglobal-hmpv-tracker-india-intensifies-surveillance-after-5-new-cases-7417332%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20reported%20seven%20cases%20of%20HMPV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20globally%20recognised%20respiratory%20virus%20that%20recently%20gained%20attention%20after%20its%20outbreak%20was%20reported%20in%20China.%20The%20Union%20health%20ministry%20on%20Monday%20said%20five%20patients%20(two%20more%20cases%20were%20detected%20later)%20have%20no%20recent%20travel%20history%2C%20and%20ruled%20out%20exposure%20from%20other%20regions%20or%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)%20has%20been%20doing%20some%20surveillance%20across%20virus%20labs%20and%20they%20routinely%20look%20at%20people%20who%20have%20ILI%20or%20SARI.%20Of%20all%20the%20cases%20that%20they%20test%2C%20about%203%25%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20positive%20for%20HMPV.%20Actually%2C%20a%20much%20higher%20number%20are%20positive%20for%20Sars-CoV-2%20that%20we%20are%20not%20talking%20about%20at%20all.%20So%2C%20this%20is%20only%203%25%20of%20the%20overall%2C%20you%20know%2C%20spectrum%20of%20viruses%20that%20are%20causing%20respiratory%20illnesses%20currently%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Swaminathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prevalence%20of%20HMPV%2C%20however%2C%20varies%20from%20month%20to%20month%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20have%20data%20in%20India%20that's%20telling%20us%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what's%20out%20there%20and%20it's%20all%20local.%20It's%20not%20that%20it's%20come%20from%20outside%20or%20it's%20come%20from%20China.%20It's%20been%20circulating%20in%20India%20for%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20seasonally%2C%20we%20are%20exposed%20to%20different%20kinds%20of%20viruses%20and%20pathogens%20and%20so%20on.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20monsoon%2C%20we%20know%20that%20vector-borne%20diseases%20like%20dengue%20start%20spreading%20more%2C%20especially%20in%20our%20cities%20and%20urban%20areas.%20In%20winters%2C%20cooler%20months%2C%20we%20see%20an%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20viruses%20and%20we%20must%20say%20that%20air%20pollution%20also%20plays%20a%20major%20role..%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMeaningless%20To%20Keep%20Count%20Of%20HMPV%20Infections%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swaminathan%20also%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bmeaningless%26quot%3B%20to%20keep%20a%20tab%20on%20the%20number%20of%20people%20getting%20infected%20in%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BIt%20(the%20figure)%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20testing%20that's%20being%20done.%20So%20if%20we%20suddenly%20start%20testing%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20have%20respiratory%20symptoms%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20find%20HMPV%20in%20the%20thousands.%20If%20we%20are%20going%20to%20test%20a%20few%20dozen%2C%20then%20we%20are%20going%20to%20find%20them%20in%20single%20digits%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20counting%20these%201%2C%202%2C%20and%203%20numbers%20is%20actually%20meaningless%20because%20we%20have%20this%20virus%20circulating%20in%20the%20community%20like%20many%20other%20viruses%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConducting%20tests%20for%20such%20viruses%20is%20more%20common%20in%20the%20private%20than%20in%20the%20government%20sector%2C%20Ms%20Swaminathan%20said.%20However%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bevery%20other%20person%20gets%20it%20and%20everybody%20cannot%20have%20a%20diagnostic%20test%20to%20find%20out%20what%20virus%20is%20infecting%20them.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20need%20also%2C%20because%20most%20of%20the%20time%20they%20are%20recovering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Relation%20With%20COVID-19%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20health%20scientist%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20correlation%20between%20HMPV%20and%20COVID-19%2C%20which%20has%20killed%20millions%20worldwide%20ever%20since%20it%20first%20broke%20out%20in%20China%20in%202020.%20%26quot%3BCoronavirus%20is%20another%20group%20of%20viruses.%20The%20HMPV%20is%20a%20very%20different%20kind%20of%20virus.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20there%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20new%20mutation%20and%20the%20HMPV%20virus%20is%20the%20same%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20China%20or%20India.%20%26quot%3BBut%20obviously%2C%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Virology%20and%20others%20are%20going%20to%20keep%20tracking%20the%20virus%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20concerned%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHMPV%20Mostly%20Unheard%20Of%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swaminathan%20said%20the%20symptoms%20associated%20with%20HMPV%20are%20very%20similar%20to%20a%20cold%20or%20a%20flu.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20that%20it's%20a%20new%20family.%20I%20think%20people%20have%20not%20heard%20about%20this%20name%20(HMPV)%20very%20much.%20It's%20not%20routinely%20tested%20or%20talked%20about%20and%20therefore%2C%20perhaps%2C%20it%20has%20come%20as%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20shock%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BDoctors%2C%20respiratory%20specialists%2C%20infectious%20disease%20specialists%20and%20scientists%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20this%20and%20have%20known%20about%20this%20virus%20family%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReinforce%20Mask-Wearing%2C%20Monitor%20Symptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20WHO%20chief%20scientist%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20wearing%20a%20mask%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20was%20enforced%20earlier%20to%20slow%20down%20the%20spread%20of%20COVID-19.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20I'd%20like%20to%20mention%20is%20that%20in%20India%2C%20we%20are%20still%20not%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20wearing%20masks%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20very%20good%20habit%20to%20inculcate%20when%20you%20have%20a%20cold%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20virus%20it%20is.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20cold%2C%20you're%20sneezing%20or%20coughing.%20Please%20wear%20a%20mask%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20infect%20others.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20concerns%20that%20HMPV%20significantly%20impacts%20children%20and%20older%20adults%2C%20the%20health%20expert%20said%20it%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bwarning%20signs%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fhmpv-in-india-are-babies-more-vulnerable-expert-answers-7419167%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20and%20it%20gets%20a%20respiratory%20infection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20if%20that%20goes%20on%2C%20leading%20to%20breathlessness%20or%20incessant%20coughing%2C%20or%20unable%20to%20take%20feeds%20or%20swallow...%20the%20child%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20a%20doctor.%20Similarly%2C%20an%20older%20person%2C%20if%20you%20find%20the%20person%20breathing%20fast%20or%20getting%20breathless%20or%20unable%20to%20lay%20down%2C%20the%20person%20needs%20to%20go%20to%20a%20doctor.%20People%20who%20have%20asthma%2C%20%C2%A0underlying%20cardiac%20illnesses%2C%20if%20the%20symptoms%20get%20exacerbated%2C%20then%20you%20need%20to%20go%20and%20see%20your%20doctor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesting%20Public%20Healthcare%20System%20Key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swaminathan%20said%20the%20prevalence%20of%20such%20viruses%20help%20to%20test%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20public%20healthcare%20system.%20%26quot%3BHow%20well%20are%20we%20going%20to%20do%20when%20we%20are%20faced%20with%20the%20real%20threat%20of%20a%20new%20epidemic%20or%20a%20pandemic.%20This%20kind%20of%20thing%20maybe%20allows%20us%20to%20test%20the%20system%20a%20little%20bit%20and%20also%2C%20maybe%2C%20put%20a%20little%20more%20focus%20on%20surveillance%2C%20genomic%20testing%2C%20and%20the%20communication%20of%20those%20results%20to%20the%20public.%20You%20know%2C%20we%20need%20good%20public%20health%20communication%20so%20that%20people%20don't%20get%20into%20these%20kinds%20of%20panic%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeasures%20To%20Fight%20HMPV%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20wearing%20a%20mark%2C%20intake%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffight-hmpv-with-hydration-nutrition-no-antibiotics-needed-ex-aiims-director-dr-randeep-guleria-7419391%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elots%20of%20fluids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20keeping%20one's%20hands%20clean%20and%20taking%20a%20paracetamol%20in%20case%20of%20fever%20and%20body%20ache%20are%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fhmpv-keep-these-dos-donts-in-mind-to-keep-yourself-safe-from-this-virus-7417704%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprecautionary%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20health%20expert%20suggested.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20become%20breathless%20and%20are%20coughing%20continuously%20and%20unable%20to%20eat%20and%20start%20vomiting%2C%20these%20are%20definitely%20warning%20signs%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%20Spread%20health%20awareness%20and%20do%20not%20create%20panic.%20Let%20us%20educate%20ourselves%20on%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20rationally%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20advised%20states%20to%20step%20up%20surveillance%20for%20respiratory%20illnesses%2C%20including%20ILI%20and%20SARI%2C%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20prevention%20of%20HMPV.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20the%20virus%20is%20already%20in%20%26quot%3Bcirculation%26quot%3B%20globally%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20no%20need%20to%20panic%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736265660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmc9cfhtg_hmpv_650x400_07_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-3-of-respiratory-cases-tested-are-hmpv-positive-former-who-chief-scientist-soumya-swaminathan-7421509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20WHO%20chief%20scientist%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%20said%20the%20HMPV%20infection%20has%20been%20in%20circulation%20in%20India%20for%20several%20years.%20Seven%20cases%20have%20been%20registered%20in%20the%20country%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-3-of-respiratory-cases-tested-are-hmpv-positive-former-who-chief-scientist-soumya-swaminathan-7421509%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billion-dollar%20potential%3A%20Haldiram's%20snack%20empire%20attracts%20global%20interest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736265427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbillion-dollar-potential-haldiram-s-snack-empire-attracts-global-interest-125010701233_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Haldiram%20brand%20which%20is%20today%20a%20household%20name%20had%20a%20rather%20humble%2