ics.%20Globally%2C%20fertility%20rates%20have%20declined%20significantly%2C%20falling%20from%20an%20average%20of%205.3%20children%20per%20woman%20in%201963%20to%20less%20than%20half%20that%20figure%20today%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F1996984%2Felon-musk-world-biggest-problem-china-india%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDaily%20Express%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20graph%20first%20published%20in%202020%20illustrates%20that%20while%20both%20India%20and%20China%20had%20populations%20of%20around%201.5%20billion%20in%202018%2C%20their%20trajectories%20are%20expected%20to%20diverge%20sharply.%20By%202100%2C%20India's%20population%20is%20projected%20to%20decline%20to%20just%20under%201.1%20billion%2C%20a%20reduction%20of%20about%20400%20million.%20China's%20population%2C%20however%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20fall%20dramatically%20to%20731.9%20million-a%20staggering%20drop%20of%20731%20million.%20This%20would%20position%20Nigeria%2C%20with%20a%20projected%20population%20of%20790.1%20million%2C%20as%20the%20world's%20second%20most%20populous%20country%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20report%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Washington%20suggested%20that%20population%20decline%2C%20particularly%20in%20China%20and%20India%2C%20might%20occur%20more%20rapidly%20than%20previously%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20fertility%20rates%20below%20replacement%20levels%2C%20the%20United%20States%20is%20projected%20to%20remain%20the%20fourth-largest%20nation%20in%202100%2C%20with%20population%20stability%20supported%20by%20positive%20net%20migration.%20Similarly%2C%20Canada%20and%20Australia%20are%20expected%20to%20maintain%20semi-stable%20populations%20through%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202100%2C%20current%20growth%20nations%20such%20as%20Indonesia%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20predicted%20to%20experience%20slight%20population%20declines%2C%20while%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%20and%20Ethiopia%20are%20expected%20to%20surpass%20them%20in%20population%20size%20around%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20has%20frequently%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20global%20population%20decline%2C%20warning%20that%20%26quot%3Bpopulation%20collapse%20is%20coming.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736260680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fm2hesq1o_elon-musk_625x300_24_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-reacts-to-projection-of-drastic-population-decline-in-india-china-7420578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20has%20taken%20to%20X%2C%20to%20share%20his%20agreement%20in%20a%20post%20that%20population%20decline%20now%20stands%20as%20the%20world's%20biggest%20problem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-reacts-to-projection-of-drastic-population-decline-in-india-china-7420578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Acceptable%3A%20Yuvraj%20Reminds%20India%20Of%20'More%20Hurting'%20Loss%20Than%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWorld%20Cup-winning%20former%20all-rounder%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20has%20said%20that%20being%20whitewashed%20at%20home%20by%20New%20Zealand%20was%20a%20bigger%20low%20for%20Team%20India%20than%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20but%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20chorus%20of%20criticism%20against%20embattled%20veterans%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%20India%20have%20endured%20a%20difficult%20last%20few%20months%20in%20the%20five-day%20format%2C%20going%20down%200-3%20to%20an%20under-strength%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%2C%20which%20was%20a%20first%20in%20the%20team's%20Test%20history.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20a%201-3%20drubbing%20by%20Australia%20in%20