-aus%2Farticleshow%2F117007887.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimesofIndia.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorkload%20management%20is%20bull****.%20These%20are%20Australian%20terms%2C%20created%20by%20Australians.%20I%20come%20from%20an%20era%20when%20cricketers%20used%20to%20listen%20to%20their%20bodies%20and%20no%20one%20else.%20I%20don't%20agree%20with%20this%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandhu%20vehemently%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkload%20management%20has%20been%20a%20big%20aspect%20of%20Bumrah's%20career%2C%20particularly%20due%20to%20his%20unorthodox%20bowling%20action.%20However%2C%20Sandhu%20took%20the%20example%20of%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20highlight%20that%20bowling%2015-20%20overs%20a%20day%20should%20not%20be%20a%20big%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20bowl%2025-30%20overs%20in%20a%20day.%20Kapil%20(Dev)%20has%20bowled%20long%20spells%20throughout%20his%20career.%20Your%20body%20and%20muscles%20get%20conditioned%20when%20you%20bowl%2C%20bowl%2C%20and%20bowl%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandhu%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20vociferous%20statement%2C%20Sandhu%20concluded%20that%20Bumrah%20or%20any%20other%20bowler%20who%20fails%20to%20consistently%20bowl%20long%20spells%20should%20consider%20giving%20up%20playing%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20you%20have%20the%20best%20physios%2C%20the%20best%20masseurs%2C%20and%20excellent%20doctors%20to%20take%20care%20of%20your%20body.%20If%20a%20bowler%20can't%20bowl%2020%20overs%20in%20an%20innings%2C%20he%20should%20forget%20about%20playing%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandhu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20participation%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20still%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20his%20recovery%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C