%20workers%2C%20and%20Noori%20often%20assisted%20them%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267251%2Fvaccinate-sex-workers-transgenders-domestic-help-free-covidactioncollab-coronavirus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20medical%20help%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20one%20such%20visit%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20Noori%20saw%20a%20poster%20on%20HIV%20and%20AIDS%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20get%20tested%2C%20and%20stating%20that%20there%20is%20no%20cure%20for%20the%20disease.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20handle%2010%20to%2015%20clients%20daily%20and%20I%20wondered%20why%20this%20was%20such%20a%20deadly%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9COn%20July%2022%2C%201987%2C%20I%20was%20the%20second%20person%20to%20be%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20spending%20some%20quality%20time%20with%20the%20kids%20at%20the%20shelter%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-elem